  "text": "SZ95 sebocytes transfected with Lv-shCon and LvshAhR were exposed to PGN (20 μg/mL). mRNA expression of TNF-α and IL-8 was detected by RT-PCR after 3 h of treatment and protein levels in supernatants were measured by ELISA after 48 h of treatment. Lv-shConand Lv-shAhR-transfected SZ95 sebocytes have been established and described in previous work [CITATION_1] . In the present study, TNF-α and IL-8 protein levels in the supernatants of Lv-shAhR-transfected cells were markedly reduced compared those of Lv-shCon-transfected SZ95 sebocytes (Fig. 2a, b) .",
